      <p>
        The shift from a manual house construction estimator to a custom software solution is the single most impactful operational move a builder can make. It transforms your pre-construction department from a cost center into a <strong>Margin Protection Agency</strong>.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Closing the Loop with Job Costing</h3>
      <p>
        The greatest weakness of spreadsheets is that they are "fire and forget." A custom software solution allows you to integrate your <strong>Job Costing</strong> data back into your estimating engine. By comparing "Estimate vs. Actual" for every project, the system becomes smarter over time, automatically adjusting waste factors and labor hours based on real-world performance.
      </p>
      <p>
